text:
Name: Katherine Miller.
Graduation Year: 2021.
Description: Katherine Miller is a dedicated Music Production student with a strong passion for innovation and learning. Throughout their academic journey, they have gained experience in music production research and practical applications. They aspire to become a mechanical engineer working on cutting-edge robotics and automation. Their dedication to excellence and problem-solving skills make them a promising professional in their field..
